      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo mehs famaitafim fcho\nWeetu/ tapehz/ ka winxo Brehe-\ntchana leela irr preekfch ta KUN-\nGA/ un tas KUNGS irr muhs\nfuhtijis to famaitaht."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Lats isgahje/ un run-\nnaja us favveem Snohteim/ kas\nwinxa Meitas gribbeja aprneimt/\nun fazzija: Zelleetes un eite nohst\nno fhahs Weetas / jo tas\nKUNGS famaitahs fcho Pils-\nfahtu / bet winxh bija favveem\nSnohteem itt ka Smeeklus run-\nnadams."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad Gaisma mettahs/\nskubbinaja tee Engeti to Lattu/\nfazzidami: Zellees / xem tawu\nSeewu unn tawas diwi Meitas /\nkas klahtu irr / ka tu eekfch fcha\nPilsfahta Noseeguma bohjā ne\nejji."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet winxch kawejahs/ tad\nfatwehre tee Wihti winna Roh-\nku/ un winna Seewas Rohku/\nun winna diwejo Meito Rohku/\ntapehz/ ka ta KUNGA Apscheh-\nlochana pahr winnu bija/ un is-\nwedde to/ un pamette to ahra\npreekfch Pilsfahta."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad tee tohs bij ahra\niswedduschi/ tad fazzija winxch:\nIsglahb jelle tawu Dsihwibu /\nne afskattees atpakkaſ/ un ne stah-\nwi schinni wiſā Klajumā / is-\nglahbees Kalnā/ ka tu jaschu boh-\njā ne ejji."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Lats fazzija us teem/\nNe/ luhsams Kungs."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rangi jelle/ taws Kalps\nirr Scheblastibu atraddis tawās"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Redsi jelle fchis Pilsfahte\nirr turvu klaht/ ka es uhs turren\nwarru behgt/ un ta irr masa/ la-\nes jelle tur glahbjohs / neggi ta\nirr masa/ka es dsihws paleefu."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winxch fazzija us to\nReds/ es arridsan schinni Leete\nefmu tew usluhkojis / ne famaita\ndams to Pilsfahtu / no ka tu eff\nfazzijis."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Steidsees / glahbees tu-\npatt/ jo es ne warru ne ko darriht\nteeſams tu uhs turren effi nahzie\nTadeht tappe ta Pilsfaht\nWahrds nosaukts Joāra."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta Saule bij uslehkusi\nkad Lats Joāra nahze."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Untas KUNGS likke wir\nSodomu un Gomorru Sehra\nun Uggunt liht no ta KUNGA i\nDebbetim."
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un famaitaja wiffai tob\npaſchus Pilsfahtus / un wiffu i\nKlajumu / un wiffus Pilsfaht\nEedsihwotajus/ ir tohs Seimme\nAngkus."
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winna Seewa afska-\nttahs atpakkaſ/ un tappe / po\nSahls-Stabbu."
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbrāims zehlahs i\nagri us to Weetu / fur winx-\npreekfch ta KUNGA Waigu i\nstahwejis."
    }
